ZODB Requires:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- new URLWidget
- new EmailWidget
- TextWidget has size_max property
- new 'help' attribute for widgets to store information related to filling the
  widgets. This information can be displayed in UI as tooltips.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
-
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- renaming properties that ending with '_str' and using '_c' for computed attribute
  _expression_str -> _expr, _expression -> _expr_c
  whatever_str -> whatever, whatever -> whatever_c
